{"tid":2513988,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中東籍男生被控8.31半周年暴動罪成 續還押至5月24日判刑","createTime":"2021-05-03T03:24:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-03T05:26:26.000Z","uid":240362,"like":5,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"8196bde4c3dce528c374dc7f715259a33cdfafb1","tid":2513988,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T03:24:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/15383\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F15383&d=LCDPOb8M8FyYKm9nuxOGtVLdO2JNS7rEhaOnhOWKq7w%3D&h=97893d0d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/15383</a><br />\n<br />\n#區域法院第卅二庭<br />\n#姚勳智法官 #聆取對控罪的回答<br />\n#20200229旺角 #831半週年<br />\n👤鈕 (19)🛑已還押逾14個月🛑<br />\n<br />\n控罪1：暴動<br />\n被告被控於2020年2月29日，在旺角西洋菜南街近豉油街一帶參與暴動。<br />\n<br />\n控罪2：襲擊在正當執行職務的警務人員<br />\n被告被控於同日，在奶路臣街近彌敦道交界處襲擊正當執行職務的警員34731。<br />\n=================<br />\n‼️被告正式在庭上承認「暴動」罪，因認罪協議，「襲警」罪會存檔法庭‼️<br />\n=================<br />\n法庭把案件押後至2021年5月24日 10:00 進行判刑，期間被告人需繼續還押看管，法庭會為被告索取背景報告，若控辯雙方希望呈上案例予法庭參考，需於5月17日前呈上法庭。"},{"pid":"55a227026fd5b5a2ee613558d55521c7b1463b05","tid":2513988,"uid":280525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T03:25:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8395780c4c35f7d10b7fd12daffaae80e6f30c9d","tid":2513988,"uid":52779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T03:25:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f5d222dd358badb31ef8997d0cf0b9f583da10c","tid":2513988,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T03:26:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/TLPWjlx4hf_AHnru4pxxeHaC7Ow=/802x498/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ESAXKCOOXMGV6WFYGMEANXEA2U.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FTLPWjlx4hf_AHnru4pxxeHaC7Ow%3D%2F802x498%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FESAXKCOOXMGV6WFYGMEANXEA2U.gif&h=108d9f65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n8.31半周年有便衣警落單在旺角遭「私了」，一度拔槍自保，到場增援的防暴警拘捕一名外籍VTC學生，指他向警員投擲水樽和用竹枝指向警員。<br />\n<br />\n控罪書上顯示被告是「中東籍」，他被控於2020月年2月29日在奶路臣街近彌敦道交界襲擊警員A。<br />\n<br />\n被告毋須答辯，本案押後待警方撿取案發現場的閉路電視片段、為目擊證人錄取口供，及索取警員A的醫療報告等。主任裁判官羅德泉拒絕被告保釋申請。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200303/O4L65FK6TUHDSPGRRULCY3JYGU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200303%2FO4L65FK6TUHDSPGRRULCY3JYGU%2F&d=LCDPOb8M8FyYKm9nuxOGtVLdO2JNS7rEhaOnhOWKq7w%3D&h=f2ffd345\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200303%2FO4L65FK6TUHDSPGRRULCY3JYGU%2F&h=598fe943\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200303/O4L65FK6TUHDSPGRRULCY3JYGU/</a>"},{"pid":"be03ab4910a5bc7e74e1ab1888463a4fab29a4c4","tid":2513988,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T03:30:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f204678a8e0f097a35c8d99cb4a39b4a513c3510","tid":2513988,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T03:32:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a98553794e8dec128082da85e9041b60c23a0bf","tid":2513988,"uid":65790,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T03:33:54.000Z","msg":"扔個水樽就暴動，唉"},{"pid":"40e982744150848761025e74c4b6104e8f1d871b","tid":2513988,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f5d222dd358badb31ef8997d0cf0b9f583da10c","tid":2513988,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T03:26:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/TLPWjlx4hf_AHnru4pxxeHaC7Ow=/802x498/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ESAXKCOOXMGV6WFYGMEANXEA2U.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FTLPWjlx4hf_AHnru4pxxeHaC7Ow%3D%2F802x498%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FESAXKCOOXMGV6WFYGMEANXEA2U.gif&h=108d9f65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n8.31半周年有便衣警落單在旺角遭「私了」，一度拔槍自保，到場增援的防暴警拘捕一名外籍VTC學生，指他向警員投擲水樽和用竹枝指向警員。<br />\n<br />\n控罪書上顯示被告是「中東籍」，他被控於2020月年2月29日在奶路臣街近彌敦道交界襲擊警員A。<br />\n<br />\n被告毋須答辯，本案押後待警方撿取案發現場的閉路電視片段、為目擊證人錄取口供，及索取警員A的醫療報告等。主任裁判官羅德泉拒絕被告保釋申請。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200303/O4L65FK6TUHDSPGRRULCY3JYGU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200303%2FO4L65FK6TUHDSPGRRULCY3JYGU%2F&d=LCDPOb8M8FyYKm9nuxOGtVLdO2JNS7rEhaOnhOWKq7w%3D&h=f2ffd345\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200303%2FO4L65FK6TUHDSPGRRULCY3JYGU%2F&h=598fe943\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200303/O4L65FK6TUHDSPGRRULCY3JYGU/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T03:35:52.000Z","msg":"Full gear 都咁撚淆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d697833e026fbcb575e74d2738a9032914556f0","tid":2513988,"uid":110043,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T03:36:49.000Z","msg":"小小事都暴動"},{"pid":"db85cbbbfcd0218e464c1cf4b2e6e2fc3a3bb014","tid":2513988,"uid":314509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T03:37:01.000Z","msg":"乜嘢叫「中東籍」？邊個國家叫「中東」？<br />\n法律文件都寫到咁含糊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1f59d0569f125582139a5c1eb48d947be76bfdb","tid":2513988,"uid":254246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T03:37:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85a53e080ce2a72402115e64cdceb73e933172c6","tid":2513988,"uid":52705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T03:42:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07b35f9ffacc4837017eb582ab59b390ced6d07b","tid":2513988,"uid":84668,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T03:46:34.000Z","msg":"南亞手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"812e5b28b0207d24dbe3ab1aab1929aa1ea28626","tid":2513988,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T03:48:35.000Z","msg":"好記得呢隻黑狗柒撚懵懵咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46a1a33cd374e7e237b816cd2b9e7a9cbb4a43dd","tid":2513988,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T04:03:32.000Z","msg":"案情指，當日大批示威者於旺角及太子集結，涉案警員遂奉命在兩區巡邏。警員便衣執勤，但穿著標準警察背心。晚上約10時許，警車巡經彌敦道與山東街交界時，目睹約十多名黑衣人在該處架設路障。警員遂與同僚下車追捕，期間有人稱警員掉了一些裝備，警員停下檢查，因而落了單。十多人隨即靠攏及襲擊警員，向其投擲雜物。警員的頭盔在過程中被搶去，更被示威者拳打腳踢至倒地。警員感覺生命安全受到威脅，遂擎槍自衛。<br />\n<br />\n被告期間先後向警員投擲竹支及水樽。警員多次嘗試突圍而出均不成功，及至其他警員到場才成功脫險。被告亦隨後被捕。由豉油街至雅蘭中心，警員至少被示威者追趕了200米。<br />\n<br />\n被告當日約晚上8時獨自到達西洋菜南街與豉油街交界，現場有大批示威者聚集。不久，他聽到有人大叫「唔好畀個警察走！」，並追打該警員。被告順勢加入，向警員投擲竹枝及水樽。警員事後到醫院求醫，醫療報告指其頭部、雙臂及雙腿擦傷腫脹，左腳踝骨折，並獲批23天病假。"},{"pid":"dd291f5f7100161e86ec41d1825b41d8b13cf94a","tid":2513988,"uid":232157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T04:03:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bde961cc2c3562505907cb127f46774667d96577","tid":2513988,"uid":45857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T04:09:02.000Z","msg":"如果量刑48個月左右<br />\n1/3認罪硬食<br />\n1/3獄中表現<br />\n14個月還押<br />\n最快今年8～9月挨完<br />\n<br />\n如果狗官玩野的佢去教導所之類，就有撚排仲要白坐14個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08863d66f7441d78aad458591e4767e33ab4994a","tid":2513988,"uid":40267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T04:11:18.000Z","msg":"乜有國家叫中東咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b916cf901c97c0676ec7a51dee3181fd3a342c6","tid":2513988,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T05:26:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}